==Mandarin==
===Etymology===
Literally: (to be so scared and paranoid, that when the wind blows the) grass and trees, (one thinks that) the (enemy) soldiers are everywhere (and are about to attack)
===Idiom===
{{PAGENAME}} (''[[Pinyin]]'' căo mù jiē bīng)
# describes a situation in which someone is being overly paranoid

